Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.72,0:24:02.33,Default - jikai,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(831,490)}总有种不祥的预感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.99,0:24:05.18,Default - jikai,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(831,490)}啊  不可以的  库奇  库拉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.41,0:24:07.36,Default - jikai,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(831,490)}这个点了还吃巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.74,0:24:09.48,Default - jikai,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(831,490)}会吃不下晚饭的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.02,0:24:12.94,Default - jikai,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(831,490)}还会蛀牙  最重要的是会发胖啊
